    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "To update the helper you need to bump it in packages/react-instantsearch.\r\n\r\nTo avoid any locking/upgrade issues, restart from v2 branch, checkout it, do `yarn boot`, the yarn.lock file should not change at all, then:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncd packages/react-instantsearch\r\nyarn add algoliasearch-helper@2.19.0\r\n```\r\n\r\nThen you should be good, right now this PR is rolling back some package to old versions and adds the helper at the root level (instead of in packages/).\r\n\r\nLet me know if you need help on this.",
